casebody.data:
James C. MCCANN, Personal Representative of the Estate of Mark Wheeler, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Yolanda GUERECA-BATANI, a/k/a Yolanda Guadalupe Wheeler, a/k/a Yolanda Guereca, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 158202
COA: 343743 Supreme Court of Michigan. February 4, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the May 23, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
